Hello! Thank you for calling Harmony Music School. My name is Douglas Walker. May I have your name, please?

Hi Douglas! My name is Sara Washington.

Nice to meet you, Sara! How can I assist you today regarding your privacy queries?

I’m excited to start classes! But I’m curious—what personal information does the school need from me?

We just need some basic information to get started. Could you first confirm your email address, please?

Sure, my email is sara.washington@example.com.

Thank you, Sara. One more thing, could you please provide your contact phone number?

Of course! My phone number is six one five, three zero zero, one two three four.

Perfect! We’ve got everything we need. Thank you so much for providing your details.

No problem! I’m looking forward to my first lesson.

We’re thrilled to have you, Sara! Thank you for your time and have a great day ahead!
